Need of API Gateways
Multiple microservices has common properties such as authentication, authorization, etc
To implement these common things we make use of API Gateway

-check application of properties file

Calling webservices Via API Gateway
http://localhost:8765/<namefromEureka>/<originalurl>
http://localhost:8765/CURRENCY-CONVERSION/currency-conversion-feign/from/USD/to/INR/quantity/10
http://localhost:8765/CURRENCY-CONVERSION/currency-exchange/from/USD/to/INR